snippet.title: Pizza Rogue Prologue: Pizza Pups Multidimensional Pizzeria Driving Evaluation Simulation Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Pizza Pups Multidimensional Pizzeria Driving Evaluation Simulation, or PPMPDES for short. Do you have the driving skills to take on a multiverse of vehicle based challenges? 
Explore 4 whole floors of the multiverse. Experience a thrilling story with real live unpaid voice actors. Enjoy.... A whole co-op system that "Technically" supports over 100 players, if  the simulations host machine can actually handle it. 
What are you waiting for? Wishlist it now: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3323710/Pizza_Rogue_PPMPDES/

Credits:
Voices:
Narrator: Arlewinn
Hajime: ‪@P0.e‬ 
Nyx:  @thegrandhighpriestess  
The Voice:  @NoaAurelyte   

Music:
background music: ‪@andrewchambersmusic‬ and ‪@SoundPhenomenon‬
